    "A few participants felt concerned about the relative emphasis on publishing AI results that seem good in theory but do not consider whether they can improve patient outcomes.",
    "The experts brought attention to the complexity of implementing AI solutions in healthcare and the importance of moving from research and development to actual deployment (Table 3).",
    "Balancing AI for different healthcare stakeholdersWhile the first theme focused on AI as an object of development, this theme explores those who shape and benefit from AI solutions.",
